node.text: Thank you @indeskribeabull I was needing this, this morning. I had to follow you. I had this same conversation with my 11 year old last night but she put it better so I made him watch this. It’s better to be consistently good than occasionally great! Also right now I’m watching a couple ppl around me thinking their shortcuts to wealth, power, success, happiness etc will help them win. “If you’re not a reliable servant he will pass you up every time.” #aintnoplug #youtheplug #tenacity #consistency #noshortcuts

node.text: 😩😩😩first day of middle school!!!! My baby’s not a baby anymore! Dropping him off and watching him walk in to get his own locker for the first time and change classes mad me a little melancholy but proud. He was a little nervous then pushed his nervous aside and walked right in — head held high. Then my oldest is in his sophomore year of college and I just dropped him off. Mannnnnn!

node.text: Me and my brother @therealsoupcampbell  my cousin @terrashockley  my friend @iamdaniwright and my tv daughter @msjenfreeman  are excited but everybody is not so happy… meet my nephew @devin_jecarl Go follow his ass and tell him Tisha sent you! Ohhhh and loved going up against @deoncole

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Tisha Campbell on August 08, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, braids, wrist watch and outdoors.

node.text: From  the moment I looked into your eyes I knew I was in love! The greatest gift I thought I could give to you was independence but you added confidence, tenacity, intelligence and kindness all on your own despite any challenges. I couldn’t raise a boy to a man on my own. If it wasn’t something I could give or teach you, YOU sought out positive role models to help guide you into manhood. Your immense desire to be a STRONG DEPENDABLE man and to take care of me, your little brother and to be a considerate, loving and trustworthy person to your girlfriend makes me PROUD! YOU just make me PROUD. Happy birthday my love…Happy birthday!
